OL,3,CCarol Vorderman reveals health battle
OL,4,Cthat left her 'unable to move'
OL,6,FTV presenter Carol Vorderman says she
OL,7,Fhas been battling with chronic
OL,8,Frheumatoid arthritis, which at its
OL,9,Fworst left her unable to move.
OL,11,FThe 64-year-old former Countdown host
OL,12,Fexplains the symptoms developed very
OL,13,Fsuddenly and says, "It was like my
OL,14,Fbody exploded".
OL,16,FShe reveals she has been receiving
OL,17,Ftreatment at an NHS rheumatology
OL,18,Fdepartment in her home of Bristol and
OL,19,Fis now on the right medication.
