OL,3,CCarol Vorderman reveals health battle
OL,4,Cthat left her 'unable to move'
OL,6,F"To come out of pain and utter
OL,7,Fexhaustion, you suddenly look at life
OL,8,Fin a different way," Carol adds.
OL,10,FThe former I'm A Celebrity contestant
OL,11,Fsuddenly stepped down from her popular
OL,12,Fradio show on LBC last October and
OL,13,Fsays this experience has made her
OL,14,Fprioritise what is important.
OL,16,F"I've had a lot of energy over the
OL,17,Fyears and I think this is like an
OL,18,Fintervention because I've always been
OL,19,Fa workaholic," Carol explains. "Now I
OL,20,Fjust think, hang on."
