OL,6,FThe presenter was speaking to ITV
OL,7,FChannel to promote the Daily Mirror's
OL,8,FPride of Britain Awards, which
OL,9,Fcelebrate the nation's unsung heroes.
OL,11,FAs its long-serving host, Carol says
OL,12,Fshe is still affected by the emotional
OL,13,Fand extraordinary stories of those who
OL,14,Fare nominated.
OL,16,F"It's just beautiful," she adds. "Even
OL,17,FI cried twice during it.
