OL,6,F"There's lots of celebrities and
OL,7,Fhousehold names, but none of them win
OL,8,Fan award and that's the beauty of the
OL,9,FPride of Britain.
OL,11,F"It's people who are kind, selfless,
OL,12,Fcourageous, brave, the best of
OL,13,Fhumankind, and they're the ones who
OL,14,Fwin."
OL,16,FThe awards ceremony, held at a red-
OL,17,Fcarpet event in Central London earlier
OL,18,Fthis week, will be broadcast on ITV1
OL,19,Fat 8pm on Thursday 23 October.
